<mjml>
  <mj-head>
    <mj-font name="Montserrat" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Montserrat:300i,400,700" />

  </mj-head>
  <mj-body background-color="#fff" width="900px">
    <mj-section>
      <mj-column>
        <mj-text font-family="Montserrat, Arial" font-size="20px" color="#D2283D">Hola Il mio nome è {!ld.IEG_Assigned_name__c}, <span style="font-weight:700;">benvenuto a don Quijote! </span></mj-text>
        <mj-text font-family="Montserrat, Arial" color="#444" font-size="15px" line-height="22px">Per poterti aiutare a programmare il corso di Spagnolo perfetto per te, vorrei chiederti</mj-text>
        <mj-text font-family="Montserrat, Arial" color="#444" font-size="14px" line-height="22px">
          <ul style="margin: 0;padding:0 30px">
            <li style="font-size:14px;font-family:Montserrat, Arial;"><b><a href="https://www.donquijote.org/it/studia-spagnolo-spagna-america-latina/" style="color:#d2283d;">In quale città</a> vorresti studiare?</b><br /></li>
            <li style="font-size:14px;font-family:Montserrat, Arial;"><b>Per quante settimane vorresti seguire il corso e quando vorresti cominciare? </b></li>
            <li style="font-size:14px;font-family:Montserrat, Arial;"><b>Hai bisogno anche dell’alloggio?</b></li>
            <li style="font-size:14px;font-family:Montserrat, Arial;"><b>Che tipo di corso di Spagnolo stai cercando? </b></li>
          </ul>
        </mj-text>
        <mj-text font-family="Montserrat, Arial" color="#444" font-size="15px" line-height="22px">Resto in attesa di una risposta e a disposizione per rispondere alle tue domande, in modo da poterti aiutare a pianificare il tuo viaggio nello Spagnolo!!</mj-text>
        <mj-text font-family="Montserrat, Arial" color="#444" font-size="15px" line-height="22px">¡Hasta pronto!</mj-text>
      </mj-column>
    </mj-section>
    <mj-section>
      <mj-column>
        <mj-text font-family="Montserrat, Arial" font-size="20px" color="#D2283D" line-height="22px" font-weight="700">{!ld.IEG_Assigned_name__c}</mj-text>
        <mj-text font-family="Montserrat, Arial" color="#444" font-size="13px" font-weight="300" font-style="italic">Consulente Accademico</mj-text>
        <mj-text font-family="Montserrat, Arial" color="#444" font-size="13px" line-height="20px">{!ld.IEG_Assigned_to_email__c}<br />T.: {!ld.IEG_Assigned_to_phone__c}<br /></mj-text>
        <mj-text font-family="Montserrat, Arial" color="#444" font-size="11px" line-height="20px">
          Calle Gustavo Fernández Balbuena, 11 | 28002 Madrid | Spain
        </mj-text>
        <mj-social font-size="15px" icon-size="30px" mode="horizontal" align="left">
          <mj-social-element name="facebook" href="https://www.facebook.com/donQuijoteSchools" src="https://static.donquijote.org/images/firmas/facebook.jpg" background-color="#fff" padding-left="0"></mj-social-element>
          <mj-social-element name="instagram" href="https://www.instagram.com/donquijote_school/" src="https://static.donquijote.org/images/firmas/instagram.jpg" background-color="#fff" padding-left="0"></mj-social-element>
          <mj-social-element name="youtube" href="https://www.youtube.com/user/donQuijoteschool" src="https://static.donquijote.org/images/firmas/yotube.jpg" background-color="#fff" padding-left="0"></mj-social-element>
        </mj-social>
      </mj-column>
    </mj-section>
    <mj-section background-color="#D2283D" padding="10px">
      <mj-column>
        <mj-image width="126px" src="http://static.donquijote.org/images/mail/CRM/dq-logo-crm.png" />
      </mj-column>
    </mj-section>
    <mj-section background-color="#fff" padding="10px">
      <mj-column>
      </mj-column>
    </mj-section>
  </mj-body>
</mjml>